The hpp has this:
/** @brief Chassis id. **/
179      const size_t id = 0;

You should be using that class variable to support multiple chassis.

Seems like we lost the lines that do the reset sensors with this latest patch set:

                    // Reset host sensors since system is off now
                    startUnit(fmt::format(RESET_HOST_SENSORS_SVC_FMT, id));
